  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Shop Manager Simulator, an immersive sim in which you will take charge of a small store, gradually turning it into an efficient retail outlet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Manage different products</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have access to a wide selection of products for sale. Monitor market trends and follow consumer interest for the greatest profit! Achieve certain goals in order to receive a lucrative contracts with influencial suppliers. Their propositions will be worth the effort!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174140/extras/87eba774b184e59d2e7d0141c8de9333.avif?t=1728049193\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174140/extras_big/87eba774b184e59d2e7d0141c8de9333.avif?t=1728049193 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hire employees</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No need to do everything yourself! Hire employees to help with cash register work, warehouse management, keeping the store clean, and other activities inside the market.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174140/extras/c971bbc622716da76befa72c918f15b7.avif?t=1728049193\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174140/extras_big/c971bbc622716da76befa72c918f15b7.avif?t=1728049193 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Acquire nearby territories</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand the territory of your store by buying out your closest neighbors. Use new territories at your discretion</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174140/extras/7ce8bd44aa7c936fd16b40ffb120c69a.avif?t=1728049193\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174140/extras_big/7ce8bd44aa7c936fd16b40ffb120c69a.avif?t=1728049193 width=800 height=452 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize your shop appereance</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the appropriate store structure and visuals to suit your own taste!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174140/extras/c45512c26a8b22d64282ec007a48d992.avif?t=1728049193\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174140/extras_big/c45512c26a8b22d64282ec007a48d992.avif?t=1728049193 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Shop Manager Simulator, an immersive sim in which you will take charge of a small store, gradually turning it into an efficient retail outlet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Manage different products</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have access to a wide selection of products for sale. Monitor market trends and follow consumer interest for the greatest profit! Achieve certain goals in order to receive a lucrative contracts with influencial suppliers. Their propositions will be worth the effort!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174140/extras/87eba774b184e59d2e7d0141c8de9333.avif?t=1728049193\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174140/extras_big/87eba774b184e59d2e7d0141c8de9333.avif?t=1728049193 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hire employees</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No need to do everything yourself! Hire employees to help with cash register work, warehouse management, keeping the store clean, and other activities inside the market.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174140/extras/c971bbc622716da76befa72c918f15b7.avif?t=1728049193\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174140/extras_big/c971bbc622716da76befa72c918f15b7.avif?t=1728049193 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Acquire nearby territories</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand the territory of your store by buying out your closest neighbors. Use new territories at your discretion</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174140/extras/7ce8bd44aa7c936fd16b40ffb120c69a.avif?t=1728049193\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174140/extras_big/7ce8bd44aa7c936fd16b40ffb120c69a.avif?t=1728049193 width=800 height=452 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize your shop appereance</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the appropriate store structure and visuals to suit your own taste!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174140/extras/c45512c26a8b22d64282ec007a48d992.avif?t=1728049193\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174140/extras_big/c45512c26a8b22d64282ec007a48d992.avif?t=1728049193 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
